Class CallUnderClassLoader<V>

java.lang.Object
  au.com.permeance.liferay.clojure.CallUnderClassLoader<V>
Type Parameters:
V - the result type of method call
All Implemented Interfaces:
Callable<V>
public class CallUnderClassLoader<V>
extends Object
implements Callable<V>

This class provides a wrapper for the Callable interface which allows the call to be executed under a different ClassLoader.

See Also:
Callable, Thread.getContextClassLoader(), Thread.setContextClassLoader(ClassLoader)

Field Summary
private  Callable<V> callable
          Stores the real callable to invoke under the callClassLoader.
private  ClassLoader callClassLoader
          Stores the class loader to invoke the callable under.

Method Summary
 V call()
          Sets the current thread's ClassLoader to callClassLoader and then invokes callable, setting the original ClassLoader back after invocation.
